HEADWORD: Puller
<hw>Pull"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, pulls.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Proud setter up and <qex>puller</qex> down of kings.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

